_isBigNumber.description: Used internally to identify a BigNumber instance.

c.description: The coefficient of the value of this BigNumber, an array of base 1e14 integer numbers, or null.

e.description: The exponent of the value of this BigNumber, an integer number, -1000000000 to 1000000000, or null.

s.description: The sign of the value of this BigNumber, -1, 1, or null.
